high_descs: Walk forward to the counter on the right
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn to the left, walk to where the bread is on the counter
Slice the bread with the knife
Walk to the side where the sink is, open the cabinet under the sink
Place the knife inside the cabinet, shut the door
Look up to where the bread is on the counter
Pick up one slice of bread
Turn right, walk to the fridge on the left
Open the fridge, place the slice of bread inside, let cool, open the fridge, pull the slice of bread out
Turn left, walk to the microwave on the right
Open the door of the microwave, place the bread slice inside, close the door
Turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Step to the left to face the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Step back and look down to face the cabinet to the right of the dish washer.
Place the knife in the cabinet to the right of the dish washer.
Look up to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn right and cross the room and turn left to face the fridge.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and remove it.
Step to the left to face the microwave.
Place the bread slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bread slice plus place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go halfway across the room and turn right to the counter with the kettle on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and go to the dishwasher.
Cut the bread on the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the knife in the cabinet below the sink.
Go back to the sliced bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right and go across the room to the fridge.
Chill the slice of bread in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the microwave on the counter.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the microwave.
